#  A menu for operations on
#  currently active window. 
#  Feel free to add more items.
#  
#  Called with left-side button
#  on window title by default 
#  (I mean in this config)

DestroyMenu WindowMenu
AddToMenu WindowMenu
+ "On &Top" WinOnTop
+ "Audo&shade" ToggleAutoShaded
+ "Undecorate and &Maximize" UndecMax
+ "Autoshade and &On Top" AutoShadeAndOnTop
+ "S&tick" Stick
+ "" Nop
+ "Force close" Destroy
